Themes for Pylitaire
=====================

Anglo Bitmap
------------

A simple, familiar and fast-loading theme, great as Pylitaire's factory default.
Made by Aike Reyer, taken from Gnome Games' Aisleriot upstream package, version 3.20.0

Files:
	anglo_bitmap.svg

Source:
	https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/aisleriot/-/archive/3.20.0/aisleriot-3.20.0.zip
	https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/aisleriot/-/blob/gnome-3-20/cards/anglo_bitmap.svg

Copyright:
	2007, 2008  Aike Reyer <aike@users.sourceforge.net>

License:
	GPL-3+ <http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html>
	Originally GPL2+, see https://bugzilla.gnome.org/show_bug.cgi?id=461267#c8


Gnome Bonded
------------

Aisleriot default, very simple and perhaps the fastest theme. Included here as
it might not be available to Ubuntu users due to branding (see Ubuntu Bonded)

Files:
	gnome_bonded.svg

Source:
	https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/aisleriot/-/archive/3.20.0/aisleriot-3.20.0.zip
	https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/aisleriot/-/blob/gnome-3-20/cards/bonded.svg

Copyright:
	Even Aisleriot devs are unsure: /* FIXMEchpe: who did the Bonded cards? */
	https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/aisleriot/-/blob/gnome-3-20/src/window.c#L383

License:
	GPL-3+ <http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html>, as Aisleriot


Ubuntu Bonded
-------------

Great-looking but slow Ubuntu-branded theme.

From branding-ubuntu source package, version 0.8, as a replacement for Gnome
Aisleriot's Bonded theme. Originally named 'gnomangelo_bitmap.svg' before 2011.

Due to a bug in branding-ubuntu package it is currently not available in
Aisleriot and might not be accessible by Pylitaire, so it is included here.
See https://bugs.launchpad.net/ubuntu/+source/branding-ubuntu/+bug/1722096

Files:
	ubuntu_bonded.svg

Source:
	http://archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/pool/main/b/branding-ubuntu/branding-ubuntu_0.8.tar.gz
	https://git.launchpad.net/ubuntu/+source/branding-ubuntu/tree/branding/aisleriot/cards/bonded.svg

Copyright:
	Mads Rosendahl Hansen <madsrh@gmail.com>

License:
	GPL-3+ (GPL-2.0+ in source)


Life and Smooth
---------------

Gorgeous but very slow theme.

Found on Gnome Look website, based on Ubuntu Bonded theme. Author claims
work is a composition of several other work available at https://www.gnome-look.org

Files:
	life_and_smooth.svg

Source:
	https://www.gnome-look.org/p/1112498

Copyright:
	jess96 ("Jess from Brussels")
	https://www.gnome-look.org/u/jess96
	Derived work, see source website for details

License:
	GPL-3 (per COPYING file in downloaded tarball)
